    "Imaging studies: CT scan or MRI biopsy: Typically, a fine-needle aspiration biopsy is used.",
    "Surgical excision: the primary treatment for pleomorphic adenoma is surgical excision and complete removal.",
    "The surgical approach may involve enucleation or partial resection, depending on the tumor's size and location.",
